subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Sooners cornerback Dominique Franks said that Florida quarterback Tim Tebow was not as good as Oklahoma’s Sam Bradford, Texas’ Colt McCoy or Texas Tech’s Graham Harrell.
